<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
<head>
  <style>
    body { font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, 'Segoe UI', Roboto, sans-serif; line-height: 1.6; color: #333; }
    .container { max-width: 600px; margin: 0 auto; padding: 20px; }
    .button { display: inline-block; padding: 12px 24px; background-color: #179299; color: white; text-decoration: none; border-radius: 6px; }
  </style>
</head>
<body>
  <div class="container">
    <h1>All out of credits!</h1>

    <p>You've used all your episode credits on PodRead. Looks like you're getting a lot out of it!</p>

    <% if @credit_pack_count > 1 %>
      <p>You've purchased <strong><%= @credit_pack_count %> credit packs</strong> so far. At that rate, a <strong>Premium subscription at $9/month</strong> would save you money â€” and you'd get unlimited episodes.</p>
    <% else %>
      <p>Want to keep going? You can grab another credit pack, or save with a <strong>Premium subscription at $9/month</strong> for unlimited episodes.</p>
    <% end %>

    <p>Premium includes:</p>
    <ul>
      <li><strong>Unlimited episodes</strong> every month</li>
      <li><strong>50,000 characters</strong> per episode</li>
      <li>Starting at <strong>$9/month</strong> (or $89/year)</li>
    </ul>

    <p>
      <a href="<%= @upgrade_url %>" class="button">See upgrade options</a>
    </p>

    <p>Thanks for using PodRead!</p>
  </div>
</body>
</html>
